an-you-see-a-little-bear.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/25691","title":"Can You See a Little Bear?","author":"by James Mayhew","description":"Little Bear journeys through an astonishing collection of magical settings, and meets many exotic animals as he drifts off to sleep. The text is a series of rhyming statements and questions which draw the child's attention into the pictures, and...","reading_age":"Reading Age: 5+","interest_age":"Interest level: 1+"},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/33829/hugless-douglas-big-sleep.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/33829","title":"Hugless Douglas and the Big Sleep","author":"by David Melling","description":""},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/30573/peace-at-last2.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/30573","title":"Peace At Last","author":"by Jill Murphy","description":"The hour is late and Mr Bear is tired. But he just can't sleep - however hard he tries, all he can hear are the noises in the house.","reading_age":"Reading Age: 6+","interest_age":"Interest level: 3+"},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/30518/animal-lullabies.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/30518","title":"Animal Lullabies","author":"by Mandy Ross","description":"Mandy Ross's original poems are fantastic, with an appealing mix of everyday language and nonsense words!","reading_age":"Reading Age: 3+","interest_age":"Interest level: 0+"},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/33989/pip-posy-bedtime-frog.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/33989","title":"Pip and Posy: The Bedtime Frog","author":"by Axel Scheffler","description":"","reading_age":"Reading Age: 5+","interest_age":"Interest level: 2+"},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/30570/zzzz_cover.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/30570","title":"Zzzzz","author":"by Il Sung Na","description":"This is a gorgeous picture book about different creatures sleeping.","reading_age":"Reading Age: 2+","interest_age":"Interest level: 4 months+"},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/34368/mockingbird-song.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/34368","title":"Mockingbird Song","author":"by Carol Thompson","description":"A beautiful retelling of the classic lullaby.","reading_age":"Reading Age: 4+","interest_age":"Interest level: 0+"},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/33623/april-2014-comp-bunny-brothers.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/33623","title":"I Heart Bedtime (Martha and the Bunny Brothers)","author":"by Clara Vulliamy","description":""},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/25526/cantusleeplilbear.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/25526","title":"Can't You Sleep, Little Bear?","author":"by Martin Waddell","description":"Little Bear just can't get to sleep because he is afraid of the dark. Big Bear is patient and brings bigger and bigger lanterns to keep away the darkness. Still Little Bear is afraid, so Big Bear takes him outside...","reading_age":"Reading Age: 6+","interest_age":"Interest level: 3+"}]}
{"id":29,"url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/children/booklists/29/","title":"Bookshine books","list_description":"Great books to share with deaf children. The Bookshine booklist aims to introduce ideas for books for children up to the age of five, based on ideas given to us by parents, teachers, children and experts.","books":[{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/30615/can-t-hear-like-you.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/30615","title":"I Can't Hear Like You","author":"by Althea","description":""},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/30537/is-this-my-nose.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/30537","title":"Is This My Nose?","author":"by Georgie Birkett","description":"This book is full of lots of faces and lots of fun!"},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/25514/orangebear-applepear.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/25514","title":"Orange Pear Apple Bear","author":"by Emily Gravett","description":"Emily Gravett's colourful yet sparse illustrations cleverly depict a bumbling bear interacting in many different and imaginative ways with the fruit mentioned in the title.","reading_age":"Reading Age: 4+","interest_age":"Interest level: 0+"},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/30609/playtime-peekaboo-.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/30609","title":"Playtime Peekaboo!","author":"by Dorling Kindersley","description":"Lots of different textures accompany clear photos of children and clean white backgrounds.","reading_age":"Reading Age: 1+","interest_age":"Interest level: 0+"},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/28686/peek-a-boo-nursery-games.jpg