ustrations complement a charming story celebrating difference, friendship, non-verbal communication and alternative views of the world.","reading_age":"Reading Age: 8+","interest_age":"Interest level: 3-6"},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/30704/moomin-and-the-birthday-button.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/30704","title":"Moomin and the Birthday Button","author":"by Tove Jansson","description":"Moomin fears that his friends have forgotten his birthday and are too busy to talk to him.","reading_age":"Reading Age: 6+","interest_age":"Interest level: 3+"},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/25585/9780141500577-1-.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/25585","title":"Guess What I Found in Dragon Wood","author":"by Timothy Knapman","description":"Dragon is excited – and just a little scared – when he finds the Benjamin","reading_age":"Reading Age: 5+","interest_age":"Interest level: 3+"},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/29246/9780141502410-1-.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/29246","title":"Jumpy Jack and Googily","author":"by Meg Rosoff","description":"Bright and bold illustrations bring humour and warmth to an unusual tale of friendship","reading_age":"Reading Age: 7+","interest_age":"Interest level: 4+"},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/27294/banana.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/27294","title":"Banana!","author":"by Ed Vere","description":"Follow the cartoon-style adventures of two monkeys. One of them has a banana and the other one wants it - but what is the magic word?","reading_age":"Reading Age: 5+","interest_age":"Interest level: 2+"},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-bo