{"id":106,"url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/children/booklists/106/","title":"Books to make you laugh","list_description":"","books":[{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/29667/who-wants-to-be-a-poodle-i-dont.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/29667","title":"Who Wants To Be a Poodle I Don't","author":"by Lauren Child","description":"Trixie Twinkle Toes Trot-a-lot Delight is a pampered poodle, who lives in luxury with her owner, Mademoiselle Verity Brulée.","reading_age":"Reading Age: 6+","interest_age":"Interest level: 4+"},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/34680/9781408339008.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/34680","title":"One Thing","author":"by Lauren Child","description":"Lauren Child's take on the art of numbers. Charlie and Lola investigate what, why and how numbers and number words are used.","reading_age":"Reading Age: 6+","interest_age":"Interest level: 4-8"},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/25307/stuck-in-the-mud.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/25307","title":"Stuck in the Mud","author":"by Jane Clarke","description":"One of hen's chicks is stuck in the mud! Hen tries to push and pull him out, but she gets stuck too.","reading_age":"Reading Age: 6+","interest_age":"Interest level: 3+"},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/31147/prince-cinders.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/31147","title":"Prince Cinders","author":"by Babette Cole","description":"Prince Cinders leads a hard life, bullied by his three big hairy brothers - that is, until one Saturday night when Cinders' luck changes","reading_age":"Reading Age: 4+","interest_age":"Interest level: 3+"},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudina