{"id":260,"url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/children/booklists/260/","title":"On the Road","list_description":"Welcome in the New Year with a collection of books about journeys, trips and discoveries in various forms. Get lost in the different worlds and the polarised travels of the various protagonists.","books":[{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/31039/in-patagonia.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/31039","title":"In Patagonia","author":"by Bruce Chatwin","description":"In Patagonia is an account of Bruce Chatwin's travels to a remote country in search of a strange beast and his encounters with the people whose fascinating stories delay him on the road."},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/27643/diamond-dust-and-other-stories.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/27643","title":"Diamond Dust and Other Stories","author":"by Anita Desai","description":"Desai's protagonists set out on journeys and find themselves suddenly beyond the pale, or surprisingly back where they started from."},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/31485/9780857560087-1-.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/31485","title":"In The Sea There Are Crocodiles","author":"by Fabio Geda","description":"First published in Italian last year, the story of Enaiatollah Akbari's journey from Afghanistan to Italy has now been translated into English","reading_age":"Reading Age: 10+","interest_age":"Interest level: 12+"},{"img":"https://artlogic-res.cloudinary.com/w_120,c_limit/ws-booktrustfileserver/usr/images/books/main_image/31043/eat-pray-love.jpg","url":"http://www.booktrust.org.uk/books/view/31043","title":"Eat Pray Love","author":"by Elizabeth Gilbert","description":"It's 3 a.m. and Elizabeth Gilbert is sobbing on the bathroom floor. Sh